| Bug | File | Change |
|-----|------|--------|
| Bug 2 | `JsonEditorPanel.tsx` | Add `initializedRef` to prevent re-initialization on `stored` changes. Remove `stored` from init effect deps. Reset ref on `storyId` change. |
| Bug 2 | `useSDUIJsonEditor.ts` | Wrap initial `SET_DEFAULT_JSON` emission in `Promise.resolve().then()` for microtask delay. |
| Bug 3 | `JsonEditorPanel.tsx` | Add localStorage fallback for `isDarkMode` detection alongside `useTheme()`. |
| Bug 1 | N/A | Already works. No changes needed. |

### Critical Files for Implementation
- `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/.storybook/addons/json-editor/JsonEditorPanel.tsx` - Primary fix target: init effect race condition (Bug 2) and dark mode detection (Bug 3)
